quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  33,9,"Imi vatendi! Rangarirai chipo chaAllah kwamuri, apo chikwata chaipokana nemi chakauya kwamuri, tikave tinotumira mhepo pamwe nemauto (ngirozi pahondo yeAhzaab) amusina kumboona. Uye Allah vanoona zvose zvamunoita"
  33,10,"Apo vakauya kwamuri nekumusoro pamwe nepasi kwenyu, uye apo maziso akave anokura achitya, moyo ikava inosvika mumitsipa. Zvekare mainge musina kugutsikana maererano naAllah"
  33,11,Ipapo vatendi vakave vanoedzwa uye vakave vanondengendeswa zvakaomarara
  33,12,"Uye apo vanyengedzi pamwe neavo muhana dzavo mune chirwere vakati: “Allah nemutumwa wavo (SAW) hapana chavakativimbisa kusara kwenyengedzo!”"
  33,13,"Uye chimwe chikwata chavo pachakati: “Imi vanhu vekuYathrib (Madinah)! Hapana zvamungavaite (vavengi)! Naizvozvo dzokerai!” Uye chikwata pakati pavo chakave chinokumbira mvumo (yekudzokera) kuna muporofita (SAW) vachiti: “Zvirokwazvo, misha yedu yakatovhurika (kuvavengi).” Asi iyo isina kutombovhurika. Asi vaisada kusara kwematiziro"
  33,14,"Uye dai vavengi vakapinda nemumativi ose (eguta), uye vakave vanokwezverwa kumiedzo (kusiya Islaam), zvirokwazvo, vaizviita uye vaizengurira zvishoma"
  33,15,"Uye zvirokwazvo vakanga vatotora chitsidzo naAllah mumashure kuti havasi kuzombotendeudza misana yavo (vachisiya Islaam), uye chitsidzo naAllah chinofanirwa kupindurwa"
  33,16,"Taura (iwe Muhammad (SAW) kune vanyengedzi vanotiza): “Kutiza hakusi kuzombokubatsirai kunyangwe mukatiza rufu kana kuuraya, uyezve hamusi kuzombonakidzwa kusara kwekanguva kadiki!”"
  33,17,"Taura: “Ndiani angakuchengetedzai kubva kuna Allah kana vakada kukurwadzisai, kana kukutumirai nyasha dzavo?” Uye havasi kuzombozviwanira muchengetedzi (kana mubatsiri) kusara kwaAllah"
  33,18,"Allah vagara vanoziva pakati penyu vanhu vasingade kurwa munzira yaAllah, uye avo vanoudza madzikoma avo kuti: “Huyai kwatiri,” ivo vasingade kuuyawo kuhondo kusara kwepashoma"
  33,19,"Vachiomera kwamuri (vasingadi kubatsira munzira yaAllah). Kana kutya kukauya kwavari, unovaona vachikutarisai, maziso avo achiudyura sekunge vave pedyo nerufu; asi kana kutya kukapera, vanokutaurai zvakanyanya. Vanoemera kubatsira muzvinhu zvakanaka. Ava ndivo vasingatendi. Naizvozvo Allah vanoita kuti mabasa avo ave marara, uye izvi zvinhu zvirinyore kuna Allah"
  33,20,"Vanofungidzira kuti maAhzaab (Zvikwata) havasati vadeduka, uye kana maAhzaab akauya (zvekare) vachashuvira kuve mugwenga vari pakati pevagari vemo, vachitsvaga nhau maererano nemi; uye kana vakava pamwechete nemi, havamborwi kusara kwepashoma"